{"tid":972263,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇偵探呢個戈職業？","createTime":"2019-01-07T09:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T07:20:28.000Z","uid":229450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae553e3031c187dbe3516a7e6699dd8e26401a9","tid":972263,"uid":229450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"香港私家偵探社應該係合法的？<br />\n但至於實際做啲咩好似真係好神秘咁。<br />\n除左查通姦尋人個啲，仲有無咩其他野做？<br />\n想成為私家偵探有無話要咩學歷？或者咩條件？<br />\n大概每日工作係做啲咩？月薪？<br />\n<br />\n真係好好奇 因為自己好想做 平時好中意推理 搵野 靠線索去追答案 好想興趣成為職業 但呢個行業好伀好神秘咁 上網都唔係搵到太多相關資料 有無行內人 或者知情嘅巴絲可以透露下？"},{"pid":"3f3e352b6cb9f22d339415a5aa867a10c8aeff57","tid":972263,"uid":179356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"會似狗仔隊？利申鳩估"},{"pid":"3979410dd37ee97e22500afe0fada83c1fe23a5b","tid":972263,"uid":8902,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"買隻黎玩下就知偵探做咩架啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtNDCRp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtNDCRp.png&h=2a1281c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a672a88daed4bceee1b40dbdcbbf14353e3ee72","tid":972263,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"應該都係通下姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ae98d04ab56e7a359b7bf2e9c95b57fdc9908d","tid":972263,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"100單有90單都係做保險工傷，<br />\n工作內容：看門口，棟樓，醫院，踩線<br />\n<br />\n無你諗到咁好玩"},{"pid":"e4306e257559ac5ade4775a42ef830c17639d329","tid":972263,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"Viu TV頭盔個節目有訪問過"},{"pid":"911931edba066e9c9ca9b2edafeb919ef4e1c056","tid":972263,"uid":185410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ae98d04ab56e7a359b7bf2e9c95b57fdc9908d","tid":972263,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime